      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_6227110978383665976.png",
                "id": "talent20966",
                "key": "因果點破",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "因果點破"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">虛影</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/a0074558f99c36e32c2a642c89000de2_7561337121306079261.png",
                "id": "talent37376",
                "key": "水中幻願",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水中幻願"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">泡影</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">泡影</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方造成技能傷害時：</span>移除此狀態，使本次傷害加倍。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/2e3cc81f7cf69d8fdf351f30e4e0993a_762113710579169310.png",
                "id": "talent33270",
                "key": "星命定軌",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星命定軌"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此角色為出戰角色，我方執行「切換角色」行動時：</span>將此次切換視為「<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">快速行動</span>」而非「<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">戰鬥行動</span>」。（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/169177528/a4683772d642e5af6323bd0a51d20fd7_566563446405640070.png",
                "id": "talent46353",
                "key": "虛實流動",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "虛實流動"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span>，耗盡時不棄置此牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>棄置此牌，造成一點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7902491567499604737.png",
                "id": "talent98813",
                "key": "虛影",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/1406b92c5115e3a534938a0d3638eeea_6813004614365347499.png",
                "title": "虛影"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_5418374843308089257.png",
                "id": "talent54015",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">快速行動</span></strong></p><p>執行了一次快速行動後，我方可以繼續進行其他行動。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">戰鬥行動</span></strong></p><p>我方執行了一次戰鬥行動後，會輪到對方行動。</p><p>打出具有此規則的手牌是一個戰鬥行動，而非快速行動。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/22/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4543182718621246855.png",
                "id": "talent29675",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "規則解釋"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
